Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.73,0:47:00.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Kidzukanai uchi ni toki no suna wa ochite yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.19,0:47:07.26,Song,,0,0,0,,Dorekurai mada koko ni i rareru ka wa daremoshiranai
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.26,0:47:10.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Atarimae ni kanji teru lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.63,0:47:14.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Daremoga sekasa re teru day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.62,0:47:20.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Hontou wa kakegae no nai dorama bakari sa
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.63,0:47:27.80,Song,,0,0,0,,Shibarareta toki ga Maki okosu inochi no shoudou
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.80,0:47:34.32,Song,,0,0,0,,Tsunaida te hanasanai Mimamotteiru yo zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.32,0:47:40.93,Song,,0,0,0,,Owaranai mada Atsui omoi moyashi myakuutsu countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.93,0:47:48.15,Song,,0,0,0,,Hakanai hodo Kagayaki mashi Mune wo shimetsukeru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.15,0:47:55.22,Song,,0,0,0,,Unmei to iu kotoba ja Katarenai suto-ri- wo
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.22,0:48:01.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Michibiku eien no kanata e
